{"tid":1705590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(戰術)罷工策略，請入","createTime":"2019-11-11T01:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T02:27:19.000Z","uid":110125,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f2a93f9fd57cbd832112a2180a10e48e8965117","tid":1705590,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:58:49.000Z","msg":"今日唔知稱唔稱得上成功，但有兩位手足中槍，實在太傷心。原因係我地唔夠人，夠人就唔洗搞成咁。所以我有以下建議。<br />\n<br />\n黎明行動必須持續，而且突發。我講過好多次，香港人奴性太重唔會主動罷工，只有翻唔到工佢地先肯罷工。<br />\n<br />\n其實罷工真係好易<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690157\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690157</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n行動上可以參考以上post，但執行起上黎都係有困難。<br />\n因為你永遠唔知有邊啲人會幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我建議每個area，十八區各區，或者每條村開個tg谷，每朝630點人數，邊區夠人邊區就可以開波。</span><br />\n因為係突發嘅，我唔信每日都重狗，當冇狗嘅時候成件事都易好多。<br />\n<br />\n交通係互相扣連的，一區塞另一區自然會塞。香港人習慣每日早起罷工，咁大罷工指日可待。"},{"pid":"f9faf4591959b25c8e6e6986e974df00e747cc0e","tid":1705590,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T01:59:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"60556ab47c863c6a829221029c183fe40384f869","tid":1705590,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:01:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e60374c4ef196e14085ce8db4424dceb992d1c3","tid":1705590,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:03:53.000Z","msg":"唔好<br />\n<a href=\"https://primitivesurvivors.com/diy-road-spikes/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprimitivesurvivors.com%2Fdiy-road-spikes%2F&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BIMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=814b9751\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://primitivesurvivors.com/diy-road-spikes/</a>"},{"pid":"77244c5e7599263eb218662594ef525bb1ac192e","tid":1705590,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:12:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b2bc1b3341fd5ba2a7c176d82e789786f70eeec6","tid":1705590,"uid":170347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:24:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n希望聽日香港人唔好忘記今日發生既事 繼續返工<br />\n既然狗都開左槍<br />\n我地唔係由佢下嘛？"},{"pid":"b9cf85f972ccc99c4329169f2faea1172036f6f6","tid":1705590,"uid":158877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T02:27:19.000Z","msg":"要塞交通 噴巴士側鏡係最低傷害最高效益<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1705705\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1705705</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n巴士站或交通燈位都可<br />\n成本極低 安全性高 速度快過set rb<br />\n事後可清潔 就算要賠錢都大把人賠"}]}